{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/study/200130_js Math Expressions/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"hong_devlog","author":"hongdev","siteUrl":"https://hong-dev.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"hong-dev/hong-dev.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":""}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"bc5db41f-8c17-5d96-bd00-5a271ff27781","excerpt":"++가 1을 더하는 것인데, ++가 뒤에 있으면 변수 할당을 먼저 실행하고 +1이 된다. ++가 앞에 있으면 +1을 먼저 실행하고 그 후에 변수할당을 한다.","html":"<ul>\n<li>++가 1을 더하는 것인데, ++가 뒤에 있으면 변수 할당을 먼저 실행하고 +1이 된다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> num <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> newNum <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> num<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">//num = 2</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//newNum = 1</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>++가 앞에 있으면 +1을 먼저 실행하고 그 후에 변수할당을 한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> num <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> newNum <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token operator\">++</span>num<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">//num = 2</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">//newNum = 2</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"[JS] Math Expressions","date":"January 30, 2020","thumbnail":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/study/200130_js Math Expressions/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/study/200130_js parameter 문제/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[JS] argument가 parameter 개수보다 적을 경우의 문제","category":"JavaScript","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/study/200130_js Math/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[JS] Math method","category":"JavaScript","draft":false}}}}}